{"tid":611351,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"天宮一號失控 中國航天工程辦公室：不知道太空站甚麼時間、墮落在甚麼地點","createTime":"2018-03-31T02:26:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-27T08:50:48.000Z","uid":174498,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"6ec0528bc9f6aabe630a290122bb9ba97c53d173","tid":611351,"uid":174498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T02:26:00.000Z","msg":"已經完全失控、無法控制的中國太空站「天宮一號」，預計會在後日愚人節（4月1日）墮落地球，西方國家的預測，全球多個人口密集城市，包括北京、日本扎幌都可能是其落點。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">中載人航天工程辦公室則稱「世上沒有預報能力」，他們現在亦不知道太空站甚麼時間、墮落在甚麼地點。</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n有美國「虛擬望遠鏡計劃」（Virtual Telescope Project）網站稱將會全程追蹤、直播，看這件8.5噸的太空垃圾將落在甚麼地點。<br />\n至今日下午4時，天宮一號的軌道已降至離地189.48公里，比昨日平均高度196.4公里，距離重返大氣層、預計開始燃燒的高度180公里所差無幾。《人民日報》旗下《環球時報》引述中國載人航天工程辦公室消息稱，「世界上目前對於航天器自由再入大氣層時的預報能力」，現在無法得悉太空站會在甚麼時間、甚麼地點，以甚麼方式進入大氣層。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180330/58014227\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180330%2F58014227&d=ab76clmwX5BnS3AadcFD1P7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=f79a4e7f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180330%2F58014227&h=b627ff55\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180330/58014227</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n儲定午餐肉，有午餐肉有閪屌！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1de48cf411ac87e6889e493bc9a4789ab3968479","tid":611351,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T02:27:53.000Z","msg":"tvb :中國可突破歐美圍堵，成最大嬴家"},{"pid":"30addde677839141ff4a8d88eb0c4f3685189a3c","t